  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 79,
   "id": "296783a9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "+-----+----+------------------+-------------------+----------------+------------------+-------------------+-------------------+-------------------+------------------+------------------+-------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+-------------------+------------------+-------------------+--------------------+-------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+------------------+--------------------+-------------------+------+\n",
      "|Class|Time|                V1|                 V2|              V3|                V4|                 V5|                 V6|                 V7|                V8|                V9|                V10|               V11|               V12|               V13|               V14|               V15|               V16|               V17|                V18|               V19|                V20|                 V21|                V22|               V23|               V24|               V25|               V26|                 V27|                V28|Amount|\n",
